This Echo Stream client plugin allows to assign extra CSS classes to the item container DOM element based on a certain criteria (like user id/role/state  or item state). It allows to apply specific look and feel for the item in the stream.

Version: 2.1 (10/28/2011)
Developed by: Echo Solutions team (Kushnir Andrew)
Documentation: http://wiki.aboutecho.com/Community-Developed-Plugins#ItemConditionalCSSClasses
